OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FThe US embassy in Saudi Arabia has
OL,8,Fbeen hit, as ITV News Asia
OL,9,FCorrespondent Debi Edward reports from
OL,10,FJerusalem
OL,12,FIsrael continued to strike Tehran and
OL,13,FLebanon's capital Beirut, as US
OL,14,Fpresident Donald Trump warned Iran to
OL,15,Fprepare for the "big wave" that was
OL,16,Fyet to come.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
