CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772637083
OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FIran and its allies have hit back
OL,8,Fagainst Israel and neighbouring Gulf
OL,9,Fstates. The US embassy in Riyadh,
OL,10,FSaudi Arabia, was attacked by two
OL,11,FIranian drones, causing a "limited
OL,12,Ffire" and minor damage on Tuesday
OL,13,Fmorning. It followed an attack on the
OL,14,FUS embassy in Kuwait on Monday.
OL,16,FThe US also ordered the evacuation of
OL,17,Fnon-emergency personnel and family in
OL,18,FKuwait, as well as Bahrain, Iraq,
OL,19,FQatar and Jordan as a precaution.
OL,26,@sD@[OUtD@EO]
