OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772637083
OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FThe Israeli military said on Tuesday
OL,8,Fit was conducting "simultaneous
OL,9,Ftargeted strikes against military
OL,10,Ftargets in Tehran and Beirut" with
OL,11,Fexplosions heard and smoke seen in a
OL,12,Fsouthern suburb of Beirut.
OL,14,FTrump said the US military was
OL,15,F"knocking the crap" out of Iran in an
OL,16,Finterview with ITV News' US partner
OL,17,FCNN late on Monday.
OL,26,@pD@SOUrD@]O]
