OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,F"I think it's going very well. It's
OL,8,Fvery powerful. We've got the greatest
OL,9,Fmilitary in the world and we're using
OL,10,Fit," he added.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FDrones hit the American embassy in
OL,18,FRiyadh, Saudi Arabi overnight, with
OL,19,Fthe attack causing "limited fire and
OL,20,Fminor material damages". There were no
OL,21,Finitial reports of any injuries.
