OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,F"The shelter in place notification for
OL,8,FJeddah, Riyadh, and Dhahran remains in
OL,9,Fplace and we recommend American
OL,10,Fcitizens in the Kingdom also continue
OL,11,Fto shelter in place," the embassy
OL,12,Fwrote on X. It added that all
OL,13,FAmericans should "maintain a personal
OL,14,Fsafety plan" and avoid the embassy
OL,15,Ffacility until further notice.
OL,17,FThe US embassy in Kuwait has also
OL,18,Fclosed until further notice.
