OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FThere were more strikes in Tehran
OL,8,Fovernight into Tuesday as the US and
OL,9,FIsrael have continued their attacks
OL,10,Fsince the killing of Iran's Supreme
OL,11,FLeader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei on
OL,12,FSaturday.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, Iran held a mass funeral
OL,15,Fceremony for 165 people killed in what
OL,16,Fit described as an attack on a girls'
OL,17,Fschool in the southern city of Minab.
OL,19,FThe crowd erupted into chants of
OL,20,F"Death to America," "Death to Israel"
OL,21,Fand "No surrender."
