OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FTuesday marks the fourth day of the
OL,8,Fwar between the United States and
OL,9,FIsrael against Iran after the sides
OL,10,Fstarted exchanging fire consistently
OL,11,Fover the weekend.
OL,13,FIranian threats
OL,15,FIran is continuing to threaten
OL,16,Fshipping in the Strait of Hormuz, the
OL,17,Fnarrow mouth of the Persian Gulf,
OL,18,Fwhich is used to transport a fifth of
OL,19,Fall oil traded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
