OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FBrig. Gen. Ebrahim Jabbari, an adviser
OL,8,Fto the paramilitary Revolutionary
OL,9,FGuard, issued the threat on Iranian
OL,10,Fstate television on Monday.
OL,12,F"The Strait of Hormuz is closed.
OL,13,FAnyone who wants to pass, our devotee
OL,14,Fheroes in the IRGC navy and the army
OL,15,Fwill set those ships on fire," he
OL,16,Fsaid. "Don't come to this region."
OL,18,FUK rebukes Trump
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@^O]xD@GOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
