OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,8,Fhis government "does not believe in
OL,9,Fregime change from the skies" on
OL,10,FMonday, in an apparent criticism of
OL,11,Fthe US president's campaign in the
OL,12,FMiddle East.
OL,14,FThe prime minister had told the House
OL,15,Fof Commons on Wednesday that he stood
OL,16,Fby his decision not to get involved
OL,17,Fwith America and Israel's initial wave
OL,18,Fof strikes on Iran, and insisted any
OL,19,Faction by the UK "must always have a
OL,20,Flawful basis and a viable thought-
OL,21,Fthrough plan".
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@]O]{D@ROU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
