PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772637083
OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FTrump had criticised Starmer's
OL,8,Fdecision not to allow American jets to
OL,9,Fdeploy from UK bases to undertake the
OL,10,Fstrikes, telling the Telegraph he was
OL,11,F"very disappointed" in the prime
OL,12,Fminister.
OL,14,FUK bases are now in play in the
OL,15,Fconflict, but only so the US can
OL,16,Fstrike defensively to protect
OL,17,Fcountries being targeted by Tehran.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@SO]
