OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FThis is understood to include the
OL,8,Fjoint US-UK Diego Garcia base in the
OL,9,FIndian Ocean and RAF Fairford in
OL,10,FGloucestershire.
OL,12,FBritish nationals abroad
OL,14,FPreviously safe havens in the Middle
OL,15,FEast, such as Dubai, have seen
OL,16,Fincoming fire and hundreds of
OL,17,Fthousands of airline passengers are
OL,18,Fstranded around the globe.
