OL,3,CFresh Israel attacks on Iran and
OL,4,CBeirut as US embassy in Riyadh hit by
OL,5,Cdrones
OL,7,FUK officials are understood to be
OL,8,Fworking on plans for the potential
OL,9,Fevacuation of more than 100,000
OL,10,FBritons from the Middle East.
OL,12,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,13,Findicated that 102,000 British
OL,14,Fnationals have registered their
OL,15,Fpresence in the region. She said a
OL,16,Ftotal of around 300,000 British
OL,17,Fcitizens are in Gulf countries
OL,18,Ftargeted by Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
